org.geotools.gpx2.gpxentities
Interface TrackSegment

All Known Implementing Classes:
BasicTrackSegment
public interface TrackSegment

Represents a TrackSegment. A TrackSegment is part of a Track. It contains two (2) or more "track points", which are represented by SimpleWaypoints.

Method Summary
 int getNumberOfTrackPoints()
          Returns the number of "track points" stored in this TrackSegment.
 java.util.List<SimpleWaypoint> getTrackPoints()
          Returns a list of the SimpleWaypoint objects that are the "track points" for this TrackSegment.
